                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Memorandum by Mr. J. Rives Childs of the Division of Near
                        Eastern Affairs</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1939-06-03">June 3,
                            1939</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Statistics of Arab immigration into Palestine are only available since 1935 as it
                    was only in that year that the three categories of “Jews, Arabs and others” were
                    substituted for “Jews, Christians and Moslems.” If the categories “Christians”
                    and “Moslems” as they appeared before 1935 are lumped together they will at
                    least afford a picture of the maximum limits of Arab immigration.</p>
